data.description: Lovely two story home with open floor plan.  Home features kitchen with granite countertops, custom cabinets and all appliances included.  This home offers three bedrooms, 2.5 baths, 2 car garage with full driveway.  Backyard has covered patio and low maintenance landscaping.  Great for active living! Nearby Duck Creek trailhead, Sam Boyd Stadium, Cowabunga Bay Water Park, entertainment, schools and freeway access.
